      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 8.2 - 老子 8.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 8.2 - 老子 8.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>水善利萬物而不爭，處眾人之所惡，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The excellence of water appears in its benefiting all things, and in its occupying, without striving (to the contrary), the low place which all men dislike. Hence (its way) is near to (that of) the Dao.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
